      </header> 
      <p> <span class="muted"><i class="icon-user icon12"></i> <a href="http://blog.newxd.com/author/admin">admin</a></span> <span class="muted"><i class="icon-time icon12"></i> 10年前 (2007-10-09)</span> <span class="muted"><i class="icon-eye-open icon12"></i> 2855浏览</span> <span class="muted"><i class="icon-comment icon12"></i> <a href="http://blog.newxd.com/1574.html#respond">0评论</a></span></p> 
